1225
02:11:34,300 --> 02:11:35,300
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da.

1226
02:11:35,300 --> 02:11:38,300
[SPEAKER_00] To je, evo, veoma interesantno.

1227
02:11:38,300 --> 02:11:48,300
